{"tid":605414,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多人唔知《門徒》劉華其實都係警方卧底？","createTime":"2018-03-25T15:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T13:21:19.000Z","uid":28938,"like":32,"dislike":166,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"a8eae72c67c7645d5c0d25a6fea6d8aa3be6fe29","tid":605414,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"昆哥(劉德華)本身係毒品調查科前卧底，俾警方派出去開電器店，暗地裡做販毒生意，幫警方捉班拆家。點知昆哥發現賺到好多錢，就決定叛變真係做毒販。<br />\n<br />\n最後果幕廁所昆哥同阿力(吳彥祖)對話，昆哥好唔明阿力賺咁多錢都決定做返警察，就係因為佢自己正正係受金錢誘惑叛變左警方。<br />\n<br />\n吳彥祖個上司，苗志華都係毒品調查科出身，同昆哥同期，因為女朋友(袁詠儀)俾昆哥搶埋，所以決心用十幾年搵證據去煮死昆哥，當中公理、私情都有。<br />\n<br />\n袁詠儀上警署見昆哥最後一面果幕，苗Sir唔俾佢地擁抱，咬耳仔，正正係因為妒忌佢地嘅愛情。而一手抱開袁詠儀，因為佢地曾經拍過拖，已經有肢體接觸嘅經驗。"},{"pid":"1f307419d43f36dbe359f3dc724b702ad1405358","tid":605414,"uid":5462,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:50:21.000Z","msg":"真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到咁仔細"},{"pid":"073f26035ee87979d1c577c9f883b1454cd50c7d","tid":605414,"uid":7854,"like":298,"dislike":0,"score":298,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:50:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/131930_64a6f0d088789b85ad50fec06b71ef08.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F131930_64a6f0d088789b85ad50fec06b71ef08.png&h=bba354da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"556970f54e7363d5595ef2eff3eb1d4a454a1704","tid":605414,"uid":26385,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:53:52.000Z","msg":"係咪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafe7876f2cdba05254e6f94cf309bf642c1a136","tid":605414,"uid":82175,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:55:54.000Z","msg":"唔好聽佢講野 唔係一陣以為你錯添呀"},{"pid":"45877606f4aa2030e6ec36c49275bca54193c8e6","tid":605414,"uid":28938,"like":77,"dislike":7,"score":70,"quote":{"pid":"1f307419d43f36dbe359f3dc724b702ad1405358","tid":605414,"uid":54