br />\nNineup 報呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T21:16:38.000Z","msg":"曼聯豬波唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160f5ce21ab01eb60244fc0f703c3ac7069057fb","tid":605414,"uid":8175,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T21:26:46.000Z","msg":"Nineup報講嫁？"},{"pid":"a6587b67bbc1a27e0410636e5092649aa6b2d98a","tid":605414,"uid":177313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T21:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e952d1aeb5cec4a478696713fb3814a791de41","tid":605414,"uid":6523,"like":108,"dislike":4,"score":104,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T22:51:45.000Z","msg":"硝酸鉀(KNO3)本身係毒品調查科前卧底，俾劉德華派出去整毒品，暗地裡扮係鎂，幫劉德華考人中學有冇讀書。點知廚師發現佢成唔到型，就決定叫劉德華自己整。<br />\n<br />\n最後果幕廁所硝酸鉀對話，廁所好唔明硝酸鉀幫佢地賺咁多錢都決定沖佢落廁所，就係因為佢自己正正係受金錢誘惑叛變左。<br />\n<br />\n吳彥祖個上司，苗志華都係毒品調查科出身，同昆哥同期，因為硝酸鉀(KNO3)俾昆哥搶埋，所以決心用十幾年搵證據去煮死昆哥，當中公理、私情都有。<br />\n<br />\n銷酸鉀見到昆哥最後一面果幕，廚師唔俾佢地擁抱，咬耳仔，正正係因為妒忌佢地嘅愛情。而一手放佢入焗爐，因為佢地曾經拍過拖，已經有肢體接觸嘅經驗。"},{"pid":"b4e406eb65e0b54c730e0ecafb89236fda41d046","tid":605414,"uid":78394,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T23:16:11.000Z","msg":"留返隻豬黎煲粥啊"},{"pid":"96b793033301af32127be5190292a0a7a0715981","tid":605414,"uid":8166,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T23:22:24.000Z","msg":"苗志華喺咪私吞海洛英，自己賣比高雄班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9ab37d6c48482edb212dd07ad9804f21ef9fa1","tid":605414,"uid":82532,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b4e406eb65e0b54c730e0ecafb89236fda41d046","tid":605414,"uid":78394,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T23:16:11.000Z","msg":"留返隻豬黎煲粥啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T23:22:38.000Z",