佢聽到苗志華個名咁嬲就知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於海關係咁叫d伙記打吳彥祖條女<br />\n應該之前都係警察 同吳彥祖警校果陣同期比佢食過<br />\n之後做臥底攞正牌中出即飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c32f4f948534d3a1693e96d044a23f65bc49f97","tid":605414,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:34:48.000Z","msg":"警察同黑社會真係好難分呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb4dde00fbdc8a0b3e294b0b467604a419f5a61","tid":605414,"uid":176304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:39:05.000Z","msg":"成個POST都有聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似之前頭D 個POST <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da4a3246d6d8b432eadbc9999cee7c174e3b468","tid":605414,"uid":104035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:41:07.000Z","msg":"其實吳彥祖本身係毒犯, 睇最尾果幕就知"},{"pid":"2c34cda105b040c83c9424b63c829d8b7a8bdfc0","tid":605414,"uid":10286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:52:13.000Z","msg":"個磅都幾重戲下"},{"pid":"ab026c0750e228bc97d56f5f16f51ec3ce84dbbc","tid":605414,"uid":48473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c03e379ba72f2acabf33f7160ba9137e6161609","tid":605414,"uid":42848,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T17:51:27.000Z","msg":"收到風昆哥老婆以前扮男人出過幾張唱片添"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:53:18.000Z","msg":"大笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"